e5b19ecf61","tid":630061,"uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T09:10:28.000Z","msg":"成龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T04:28:16.000Z","msg":"成龍真係算數吧喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都一把年紀，己經去中國發展。<br />\n無錯佢係國際知名，但係佢唔係靠演技而係靠功夫以及拍電影嘅態度。<br />\n以往都有唔少人進軍荷里活，好似李連杰、周潤發、李安、洪金寶、吳宇森等，但係全部都返番中港台。"},{"pid":"e55d1fd1bbf5adfc817728aea7c8d4c21c6f20e3","tid":630061,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T17:41:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}